snippet.title: Salty Nerd Listener Questions - Hollywood After Coronavirus & Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard
snippet.description:
The Salty Crew answers questions from listeners about the state of Hollywood after the coronavirus epidemic has passed, and the fallout behind the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard divorce.
